description: This dashboard provides a high-level overview of your Clickhouse Server hosts.
title: Clickhouse Overview

eaf65de3-20bb-4dbc-9792-32a445f7be8f.name: host.name
eaf65de3-20bb-4dbc-9792-32a445f7be8f.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'host.name') AS host.name
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'ClickHouseMetrics_VersionInteger' and __normalized=false 
GROUP BY host.name
